4.8 OEAssignHybridization 
 
   
bool OEAssignHybridization(OEMolBase &amp;mol)
    
Predict the electronic hybridization/geometry of each atom from simple
connectivity.  This function updates the hybridization property of each
atom in the molecule.  See OEAtomBase::GetHybridization and
OEAtomBase::SetHybridization.

  

  
          
     
        
